<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.8.2">
<l>muṉṉivvu lakēḻumiruḷ maṇṭi yuṇṇa muṉivaroṭu tāṉavarkaḷ tikaippa vantu</l>
<l>paṉṉukalai nālvētap poruḷai yellām parimukamā yaruḷiyavem paramaṉ kāṇmiṉ</l>
<l>cennelmali katirkkavari vīcac caṅka mavaimuralac ceṅkamala malarai yēṟi</l>
<l>aṉṉamali peṭaiyōṭu mamaruñ celvat taṇiyaḻuntūr niṉṟukanta vamarar kōvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our supreme lord who, long ago when the seven worlds</l>
<l rend="indent">were bound in darkness, when sages and demons were bewildered,</l>
<l>Coming with a horse’s face, bestowed all the meaning of the four Vedas</l>
<l rend="indent">and declared knowledge,</l>
<l>Behold, is the king of immortals who is happy</l>
<l rend="indent">standing in lovely, prosperous Aḻuntūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">where a [male] swan rests along with [his] fulfilled hen,</l>
<l>Having clambered onto a red lotus blossom,</l>
<l rend="indent">as full stalks of red paddy wave[-like] fans</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] as conch shell [trumpets] sound.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
